title: Defiance TV Show/ Game Theme for Windows 7/8
description:
This is just a theme i put together for windows 7 and 8.

Try it if you want.

Files included are:

Defiance.deskthemepack
Defiance Intro.scr
How To.txt
iview436_setup.exe
irfanview_plugins_436_setup.exe

The last two files are Irfanview and the complete plugins from irfanview.net.
Wasnt Sure if you needed those since the screensaver is made with it.

Let me know what you think, I am going to get some sounds and cursors to use also!
